@rossi_davide How many cases are there of DJs entering Japan?

This is a silly meme.  If Japan let in one student for each DJ, it would not reduce the student backlog in a meaningful way.

A better example that I am investigating is "Singin' In The Rain."  It looks like a whole troop got in.

@itsmargarethall Singin' in the Rain
All That Jazz
The 1961 West Side Story. I respect many of the concerns people have raised about it. But there is no way to truly appreciate how revolutionary that show is without seeing Jerome Robbins' choreography. It's so thrilling. https://t.co/FldUVBZfjw
